{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_12_03",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 3話 チョコがついてるわよ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "あの時のバレンタイン当日、全然渡せなくて\n結局夜になっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On that Valentine’s Day‚ I couldn’t give it to you at all.\nBefore I knew it‚ it was already night…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.3655102412
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、渡さずに帰ることも出来なくて……\n事務所の前で、もじもじしてたんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I couldn’t bring myself to go home without giving it to you…\nSo I ended up fidgeting around in front of the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshifacade-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.8858053525
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshifacade-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.8858053525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん……？！\nこんな遅い時間まで、どうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san…?!\nWhat are you doing out this late?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshifacade-00-night",
      "startTime": 20.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}君……あの、あのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-kun… um‚ you see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "……頑張れ遙子っ、逃げるな遙子っ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hang in there‚ Haruko! Don’t run away‚ Haruko…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ここで逃げたら、もうっ、チャンスは……！\n……あのね、{user}君！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I run away now‚ I’ll lose my chance…!\n…Hey‚ {user}-kun!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshifacade-00-night",
      "startTime": 37.4751238506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんですか遙子さん\n今日、なんだか様子がおかしいですけど……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what’s wrong‚ Haruko-san?\nYou seem kind of strange today…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "様子なんてどうでもいいの！\n……じゃなくて、これ……もらってくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That doesn’t matter!\n…No‚ that’s not it—will you take this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshifacade-00-night",
      "startTime": 47.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshifacade-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.3152823448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これって……チョコレート？\nあ……今日はバレンタイン、でしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-is this… chocolate?\nOh… right‚ today is Valentine’s Day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そういえばそうね。いつもお世話になってるから！\nその、それだけで、これは義理のやつだから……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah‚ I guess it is. You’re always taking care of me‚ so!\nTh-that’s all—this is just friendship chocolate…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshifacade-00-night",
      "startTime": 73.1941711426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それでも嬉しいです。ありがとうございます\nあの、良かったら今食べてもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ I’m happy. Thank you very much.\nUm‚ would it be okay if I ate it now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1269812169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshifacade-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.369817416
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "い、今！？　……溶かして固めただけだし\nそれはちょっと、恥ずかしい……けど……い、いいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-now!? …I just melted it and let it harden‚\nso that’s kind of embarrassing… but… o-okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshifacade-00-night",
      "startTime": 94.9376627923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "やった、いただきます。……うまい！\n疲れた脳にしみます、めちゃくちゃ美味しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I’ll dig in… wow‚ it’s good!\nIt’d really hits my tired brain—this is so delicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 462.33720770000275,
          "startTime": 95.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "これ、遙子さんが作ったんですか？\nうまい……なんだこれ、売ってるチョコよりうまいぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you make this‚ Haruko-san?\nIt’s amazing… what is this? It’s better than store-bought!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshifacade-00-night",
      "startTime": 116.2388204576
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "ぷっ……あはは、何それ、大げさだなぁ\nふふ、でも喜んでくれて良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pfft… ahaha‚ what’s that? You’re exaggerating.\nFufu‚ but I’m glad you liked it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.2666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.3144439698
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.3144439698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、美味しいって言ってもらえたのが嬉しくて\n{user}君に夜食を作ってみたりもしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hearing you say it was delicious back then made me really happy.\nI even tried making you late-night snacks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "まさか俺が、遙子さんの青春の一部だったとは……\n驚きましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never thought I’d be part of your youth‚ Haruko-san…\nThat really surprised me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2368320203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.9937122028
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "長い話に付き合ってくれて、ありがとうね\n……ところで、あの時のお返しはいつくれるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for listening to my long story.\n…By the way‚ when are you going to give me my return gift from back then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.3333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　お返し？　……そ、それは……忙しくて\nすっかり忘れてました、すみません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? A return gift? …W-well‚ I was busy…\nI completely forgot—sorry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.9666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.7596528054
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君からの手作りチョコのお返し\nあの時から、ず～～っと待ってるからね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been waiting for your handmade chocolate\nfor a loooong time‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.4000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ！　ホワイトデーとは言わずすぐお返しします！\n何年も待たせてしまって本当にすみません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I won’t even wait for White Day—I’ll give it to you right away!\nI’m really sorry for making you wait for years!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.6889093719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.1990174931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、楽しみにしてるわね。でも、甘酸っぱい憧れの\n気持ちを思い出したからかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I’m looking forward to it. Maybe it’s because I remembered those\nsweet-and-sour feelings of admiration.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.0333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.2666681926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "制服風の衣装も、いいかもって思えてきたわ\nよぉし、今度のバレンタインCMの撮影、頑張るわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m starting to think the school-uniform-style outfit might be nice too.\nAlright! I’ll do my best at the upcoming Valentine’s CM shoot!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.2666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――CM撮影終了後",
      "translations": {
