      "text": "{user}君、撮影どうだったかな？\n結構うまくいったかなって思うんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-kun‚ how was the shoot?\nI think it went pretty well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.3666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はい。遙子さん発案のチョコを作るシーン、料理に\n慣れてることもあって凄く絵になってましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The scene where you made the chocolate you came up with\nwas really great. Probably because you’re used to cooking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.7333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 210.5848976772
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
