      "text": "ふふ、ありがと。ところで{user}君\n……私の制服姿は、大丈夫だった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ thanks. By the way‚ {user}-kun…\n…Was my uniform outfit okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.4333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 219.7368026416
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん。バッチリ似合ってましたよ\nやっぱり現役高校生でいけるんじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. It suited you perfectly.\nYou could totally pass as a current high school student.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.0666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんの手作りチョコをもらえる人は\nきっと幸せでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoever gets your handmade chocolate\nmust be very happy‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.8290536471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 232.0702942212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "どの口が言うかな、まったく……でも、この前\n{user}君と思い出話をしたおかげかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look who’s talking‚ honestly… But still‚\nmaybe it’s thanks to reminiscing with you the other day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.6000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 240.7268931389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
