      "text": "そのことなんですけど……すみません、遙子さん\nまだ、俺からのチョコ、用意が出来ていなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About that… I’m sorry‚ Haruko-san.\nI still haven’t prepared your chocolate yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.3000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "その……チョコを、レンジで溶かそうとしたら\n大爆発してしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… when I tried melting the chocolate in the microwave‚\nit exploded…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.8333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
