      "text": "えっ？　{user}君は大丈夫だったの！？\n火事とか火傷とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? Were you okay‚ {user}-kun!?\nA fire‚ burns‚ anything like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.8000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "はい、大丈夫でしたけど……レンジが壊れちゃって\n家でチョコを作れなくなっちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I was fine… but the microwave broke‚\nso I can’t make chocolate at home anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.7000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 270.6285483995
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
