      "text": "そういうことなら……今からここで一緒に作らない？\nまだ材料も残ってるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that’s the case… why don’t we make it together here?\nWe still have ingredients left.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 277.2000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
