      "text": "……実は、手作りする自信がなかったので助かります\nそれじゃあ、お願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Honestly‚ I wasn’t confident about making it myself‚ so that helps.\nThen‚ please!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.7333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、{user}君\nゆっくり丁寧に混ぜて……うん、上手ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ right‚ {user}-kun.\nStir slowly and carefully… yes‚ you’re doing well.",
