      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり、遙子さんは料理上手ですね\n一緒にやったら、ちゃんとチョコが溶かせましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You really are good at cooking‚ Haruko-san.\nDoing it together‚ I managed to melt the chocolate properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.6666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、こんなの慣れたら誰でも出来るわよ\nでも……実はね、私が料理が好きになったのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ once you’re used to it‚ anyone can do this.\nBut… the truth is‚ the reason I came to like cooking is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.9000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
