      "text": "……君のおかげなの。あの時、凄く美味しそうに\nチョコを食べてくれて……夜食もただのおにぎりなのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…thanks to you. Back then‚ you ate the chocolate\nlike it was delicious… and even though the late-night snacks",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 319.2000055949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
