      "text": "ちょっと照れますね……でも、バレンタインのチョコも\n遙子さんが俺のことを心配して作ってくれた夜食も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a bit embarrassing… but both the Valentine’s chocolate\nand the late-night snacks you made out of concern for me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 337.4000035603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_03-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "本当に美味しかったですよ。特にあの時の俺には凄く\nありがたかったです……あっ！　ちょ、チョコが……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "were really delicious. I was really grateful\nback then… ah! T-the chocolate…!",
        "id": ""
      },
