      "text": "ふふ、ありがとう、{user}君\n君は相変わらず、ずっとまっすぐで、優しいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ thank you‚ {user}-kun.\nYou’re still as straightforward and kind as ever.",
